<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KA THUP TUAH CH48</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A hmun lung-pi hun cia a um, Ka thup tuah, Sifah re-theihnak a tampi,
 Ka thup tuah, Bawipa dawtnak ka lungchung ah, Mi thlen khawh lonak hmun
 ah khan, Zungzal a fek lungpi chungah, Ka thup tuah.

[V2]
 Sualnak ram ka phak nak hnga lo, Ka thup tuah, Bawipa chungah a
 zungzal in, Ka thup tuah, Vawlei cung sunparnak chungah, Sualnak nih a ka
 forh lio ah, A hmun zungzal lungpi chungah, Ka thup tuah.

[V3]
 Ngaihchiatnak khua a muih lioah, Ka thup tuah, Sunparnak khua a dei
 hlan tiang, Ka thup tuah, Jordan tilet ka nai tkah, Na tang chungah ka
 luh ter tuah, A hmun zungzal lungpi chungah, Ka thup tuah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>48</hymn_number>
</song>